 sentence\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"30 years imprisonment\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The prosecutor's office released no further details as to what the man was allegedly planning.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The prosecutor's office\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"no further details\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Games begin this week with the official opening ceremony due to be held in central Paris on Friday evening.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999955891781, \"rank\": 4.410824902409049e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"the official opening ceremony\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday evening\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin said last week that some 4,000 people had been refused permission to attend events tied to the Olympics, with authorities \\\"paying particular attention to Russian and Belarusian citizens.\\\"\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_the_Interior_(France)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999108695, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Interior Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_the_Interior_(France)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_the_Interior_(France)\"}, {\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_the_Interior_(France)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999108695, \"rank\"